    "body": "Many thanks, that looks fine for me.\n\n@murgatroid99, One practical question then: On the node grpc client side, here is how I load the **root CA.crt**:\n\n``` javascript\nsslCaCrt = fs.readFileSync(sslCaCrtPath);\nconst sslCreds = grpc.credentials.createSsl(sslCaCrt);\nconst grpcClient = new myProto.myPackage.myService(serverURL, sslCreds, clientOptions);\n```\n\nBut in case I want my client to use **the bundled root CA.crt from Mozilla** without me telling him the path, what the code will looks like? Thanks\n"
